# The textbook ships as compiled PDFs only.
# LaTeX sources (tex/), figures/, _shared/ notes, and all build
# artifacts (*.aux, *.log, *.toc, *.out, *.fls, *.fdb_latexmk, ...)
# are kept locally but not committed.
#
# Ignore everything in this directory, then re-include just the PDFs.
*
!*.pdf
!.gitignore
